description: This Chainlink VRF common Gaston purrs with a rating of 27, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 54, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Stringalong for East, 1 for South, and 8 for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60272-17180-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [54 Votes, Common]
